data.title: Ronnie McDowell
data.meta_description: Ronnie McDowell. Music Department: Unbekannte Dimensionen. Ronnie McDowell was born on 26 March 1950 in Portland, Tennessee, USA. He is an actor and writer, known for Unbekannte Dimensionen (1985), Welcome to Paradise (2007) and Elvis und der Präsident (1997). He has been married to Karen McDowell since 15 May 1973.
data.text: Ronnie McDowell was born on March 26, 1950 in Portland, Tennessee, USA. He is an actor and writer, known for Unbekannte Dimensionen (1985), Welcome to Paradise (2007) and Elvis und der Präsident (1997). He has been married to Karen McDowell since May 15, 1973.
